BitMarket,is,a,Bitcoin,exchange,platform,that,allows,users,to,buy,and,sell,Bitcoins,in,a,variety,of,currencies,The,BitMarket,API,allows,users,to,submit,REST,requests,to,get,the,market,volume,min,and,max,prices,for,all,currencies,get,active,currency,offers,and,get,latest,completed,transactions,An,account,is,required,with,service,and,SSL,is,used,for,authentication